# Database Performance Rules

## Query Optimization
- Always use eager loading (with)
- Avoid N+1 queries strictly

## Indexing Rules
- Index all foreign keys
- Index frequently filtered columns

## Query Rules
- No DB::raw unless approved
- Avoid heavy joins in API layer

## Caching Strategy
- Cache heavy read queries using Redis
- Use cache tags for grouped invalidation

## Pagination
- Always paginate large datasets